api_list.description:
This will be a post request and body should have a json property called " **hl7Text** ". 
Value for the above key should be a valid HL7 2.x message and should have proper line break on every segment of the message. for example:
{
  "hl7Json" : " Segment 1 /n Segment 2 /n Segment 3"
}
